    • getProcedures

      The retrieval of FHIR UkbProcedure resources. The input resources are needed for a preprocessing filtering in the acuwave sided procedure data retrieval.
      Parameters:
      listUkbEncounters - A list of all FHIR encounter resources of the detected patients after a specified cut-off date.
      listUkbLocations - A list of all FHIR location resources that are referenced in any encounter resources.
      listUkbObservations - A list of all FHIR observation resources that include a covid finding.
      listUkbConditions - A list of all FHIR condition resources that include a covid diagnosis.
      Returns:
      A list of all requested FHIR procedure resources that contain artificial ventilation data for patients with at least one covid observation and/or covid diagnosis.
